Subject: Re: [T2]  A junkyard motor

Since it is so complete do a compression test before you give over some 
cash. If it is VERY complete then run it.

Beware that the engine may be thrashed badly or built so with such wild 
modifications that it is not usable on the street (wild cam, wild heads, 
etc.).

Good luck.



